
         Upgrading Instructions for PHPReq v.1.0.0
         =========================================

!!!IMPORTANT!!!

The following upgrading instructions are cumulative. That is,
if you want to upgrade from version A to version C and there is
version B between A and C, you need to following the instructions
for both A and B.

General upgrade intructions
---------------------------
- Make a backup.
- Replace 'phpreq' dir with the new one or point SVN to a fresh
  release and update.
- Check if everything is OK, if not â€” revert from backup and post
  issues to PHPReq issue tracker.

Upgrading from v1.0.0
---------------------
- First release.
